	<event name="LANIUS_DOOR" unique="false">	<!--TODO: Polish Lanius Door event-->
	   <text>Upon arriving at the beacon, you spot a massive Lanius structure. You presume it must have been drifting for years to have traveled this far.</text>
	   <choice hidden="true">
		  <text>Shoot at the structure.</text>						<!--Attack-->
		  <event>
			 <text>You fire on the structure. Suddenly, it powers up! A large weapon extends from an opening in the top, and from a hatch in the side a Lanius ship hurtles towards you!</text>
			 <environment type="PDS" target="player" />
			 <ship load="DOOR_DEFENDER" hostile="true" />
		  </event>
	   </choice>
	   <choice hidden="true">
		  <text>Hail the structure.</text>							<!--Don't Attack-->
		  <event>
			 <text>You hail the structure, and attempt to explain who you are and why you're there. A Lanius voice stops you, "Quiet! Sleeping. Leave or die."</text>
			 <choice hidden="true">
				<text>Explain what brought you here.</text>		<!--Ok option-->
				<event>
				   <text>You explain how you obtained a strange orb and that a Lanius had told you how to reach this place. The voice begins to interrupt you again, but upon hearing your words replies coldly, "Give. NOW."</text>
				   <choice hidden="true">
					  <text>Give up the orb.</text>			<!--Repair-->
					  <event>
						 <text>You allow a very angry Lanius to board your ship and remove the orb from your possession. It reluctantly thanks you for "Finding precious." and applies a metallic paste to the hull of your ship.</text>
						 <damage amount="-5" />
					  </event>
				   </choice>
				   <choice hidden="true">
					  <text>Negotiate.</text>				<!--Crew-->
					  <event>
						 <text>The Lanius angrily replies, "Fine." They come aboard your ship and take the orb. After safely putting the orb away, a single Lanius returns to your ship. It sleepily tells you, "Greetings... I am trade... Reluctant."</text>
						 <crewMember repair="1" amount="1" class="anaerobic">Trade</crewMember>
					  </event>
				   </choice>
				   <choice hidden="true">
					  <text>Refuse.</text>					<!--Attack-->
					  <event>
						 <text>The Lanius becomes angry, "NO. STUPID STUPID SCAV-FRIEND. TAKE."</text>
						 <ship load="DOOR_DEFENDER" hostile="true" />
					  </event>
				   </choice>
				</event>
			 </choice>
			 <choice hidden="true">
				<text>Attack the structure.</text>				<!--Attack-->
				<event>
				   <text>Indignant at the Lanius' response, you open fire. Suddenly, the structure powers up, and from a hatch in the side a Lanius ship emerges to attack!</text>
				   <environment type="PDS" target="player" />
				   <ship load="DOOR_DEFENDER" hostile="true" />
				</event>
			 </choice>
			 <choice hidden="true">
				<text>Leave.</text>								<!--Back Out-->
				<event>
				   <text>May as well let sleeping Lanius lie. You power up your drive and prepare to jump away.</text>
				</event>
			 </choice>
		  </event>
	   </choice>
		<choice hidden="true" req="anaerobic">
		  <text>(Lanius Crew) Ask the Lanius what to do.</text>		<!--"Correct" answer-->
		  <event>
			 <text>Your crew-member holds out the metal orb and instructs the crew to bring the ship closer to the structure. As you approach, a gargantuan hatch opens in front of you.</text>
			 <choice hidden="true">
				<text>Enter the structure.</text>
				<event>
				   <text>Once inside the structure, the hatch shuts behind you. You are surrounded by dormant Lanius ships as well as hundreds of Lanius sleeping pods. A small party of Lanius come aboard your ship, and your crew-member chats happily with them, showing off the orb. The Lanius turn to you and say "Thanks much. Name your gift."</text>
				   <choice hidden="true">
					  <text>A new ship.</text>					<!--Unlock Uber Lanius Ship-->
					  <event>
						 <text>"Yes. Agree." One of the Lanius ships, different from the rest, powers up and begins to slowly hover towards you. From inside, a Lanius hails you, "We send. Federation make changes. Get ship with air... Ok?" Without waiting for a response, the ship exits the structure and jumps away, back towards where you came from.</text>
					  </event>
				   </choice>
				   <choice hidden="true">
					  <text>Some new crew.</text>				<!--Get 3 new crew-->
					  <event>
						 <text>"Yes. Will join." The Lanius simply stand around, waiting to be given orders.</text>
						 <crewMember combat="1" amount="1" class="anaerobic" />
						 <crewMember combat="1" amount="1" class="anaerobic" />
						 <crewMember combat="1" amount="1" class="anaerobic" />
					  </event>
				   </choice>
				   <choice hidden="true">
					  <text>Anything you can spare.</text>		<!--Fuel and Missles-->
					  <event>
						 <text>"Yes. Give." The Lanius give you large containers of fuel and a number of missiles. One Lanius jokes with your crew-member, "Do not consume. 'Too spicy'... as Human speak."</text>
						 <autoReward level="HIGH">fuel_only</autoReward>
						 <item_modify>
