						 <text>The Lanius' good spirits dissolve instantly. "Yes... Scav-thief... Scav-creature can have parts." The Lanius begrudgingly allow your Scav crew-member to take some pieces from a few dormant Lanius ships and the Scav quickly cobbles them together into upgrades for your ship.</text>
						 <autoReward level="HIGH">augment</autoReward>
						 <damage amount="-3" />
					  </event>
				   </choice>
				</event>
			 </choice>
		  </event>
	   </choice>
	   <choice hidden="true">
