	<event name="SCAV_SCAVENGING_QUEST" unique="true">				<!--Unlocks the Junkyard-->
	   <text>As you approach the beacon you are hailed by a young Scav in a repurposed mining ship, painted in Federation colors. It's modulated English crackles and breaks over the comms: "Woah!! Is th#t a real =####= class-sh#p? Wait... y#u guys must be F#deration! RADICAL!!! I r##lly need- =###############= -and I'll even pay! I got- =#######= -What do y#u say? Please?"</text>
	   <ship load="SCAV_SHIP" hostile="false" />
	   <choice hidden="true">
		  <text>Sure thing bro!</text>								<!--Start Scenario-->
		  <event>
			 <text>The Scav's comms let out an electronic squeal before shutting off. Without warning, the Scav begins to attack! It's stripping random electronics out of your shield systems.</text>
			 <damage amount="2" />
			 <damage amount="2" system="shields" effect="breach" />
			 <choice hidden="true">	
				<text>Defend yourself!</text>						<!--Fail #1-->
				<event>
