				   <ship hostile="true" />
				</event>
			 </choice>
			 <choice hidden="true">
				<text>Let the Scav continue.</text>					<!--Continue #1-->
				<event>
				   <text>You reassure the crew. Surely this Scavenger wouldn't be so bold as to try and destroy your ship. It's now taking parts from your weapons system</text>
				   <damage amount="3" />
				   <damage amount="1" system="weapons" effect="breach" />
				   <choice hidden="true">
					  <text>Stop it!</text>							<!--Fail #2-->
					  <event>
						 <text>You can't bear to watch this Scavenger destroying your ship. You ready your weapons.</text>
						 <ship hostile="true" />
					  </event>
				   </choice>
				   <choice hidden="true">
					  <text>Just let it keep going.</text>			<!--Continue #2-->
					  <event>
						 <text>The Scav is destroying your engines now. Will it ever finish?</text>
						 <damage amount="2" />
						 <damage amount="3" system="engines" effect="random" />
						 <choice hidden="true">
